  "text": "Found 6 Java source files in apache/flink's flink-streaming-java/src/ directory with @Deprecated annotations.\n\nCore DataStream API Deprecations (3 files):\n\n1. AscendingTimestampExtractor (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - A timestamp assigner and watermark generator for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No explicit replacement is documented in the javadoc, but it implements WatermarkStrategyWithPeriodicWatermarks which may be the recommended approach.\n\n2. TextInputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - Input format that reads text files. Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. Recommendation from javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop the supports for read/write via input/output format in DataStream api.\"\n\n3. TextOutputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - A FileOutputFormat that writes objects to text files. Deprecated in favor of FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. Recommendation from javadoc: \"If you want to read/write data from/to text file, please use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink. This class should be removed if we drop all supports for InputFormat and OutputFormat\"\n\nTest Infrastructure Deprecations (3 files):\n\n4. OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Test harness for testing OneInputStreamTask. Deprecated in favor of StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder.\n\n5. StreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java) - Base test harness 